improvements:
estimada secretaria de relaciones exteriores.

visitando su pagina de internet me encuentro con mucha informacion desordenada que confunde, sobre todo al personal por primera vez.
quiza para mejorar deberian ser mas concisos con la informacion, que este mas ordenada y quiza con un tipo de manual que indique los pasos uno por uno que debes de seguir, un cuadro conceptual o de menos enumerarlos por ejemplo:
¿quieres obtener tu pasaporte?

paso 1.
llamar al 01800... solicitar tu cita (tener a la mano curp)
paso 2.
imprimir el acuse de tu cita y obtener el pago de tal pagina o pagar en la oficina donde vas a realizar el pago, o en el banco o etc.
paso 3 
acudir a tu cita con lo siguientes documentos:
primera vez: tales.
renovacion: tales. 
paso 4

esperar tu pasaporte o felicidades ya tienes pasaporte.

quiza crearia menos confusion y menos llamadas al centro de atencion. cuentan con el area de comunicacion para realizar el diseño y tener en una sola pagina, toda la informacion.

gracias por su atencion
andres huitron covarrubias.
huitroncovarrubias@outlook.com
missing_info_en: information missing: Where to get the payment? How to get the payment? Where can you pay the payment? How much time do you have to pay?  In addition, information is lacking on whether the service of photographs, copies, etc. is provided in the delegations or in the offices of foreign relations, if its costs.  I consider the information important.
improvements_en: Dear Secretary of Foreign Relations.  visiting your website I find a lot of disorderly information that confuses, especially the staff for the first time. Perhaps to improve they should be more concise with the information, that it is more organized and perhaps with a type of manual that indicates the steps one by one that you must follow, a conceptual table or less to list them, for example: Do you want to get your passport?  step 1. call 01800 ... request your appointment (have curp handy) Step 2. print the acknowledgment of your appointment and obtain payment from such page or pay at the office where you are going to make the payment, or at the bank or etc. step 3 keep your appointment with the following documents: first time: such. renovation: such. Step 4  wait for your passport or congratulations you already have a passport.  Perhaps it would create less confusion and fewer calls to the limelight. they have the communication area to carry out the design and have all the information on one page.  Thanks for your attention Andrés Huitron Covarrubias. huitroncovarrubias@outlook.com

improvements:
tuvimos en septiembre -al no poder pasar la revista telefonica- que ir a la secretaria de marina, pues por nuestro domicilio (en coyoacan) es lo mas facil, llegamos a la oficina de atencion y las dos personas que estan ahi nos dijeron que teniamos que ir otra vez al banco y hacer el tramite de grabacion nuevamente,fuimos al banco ahi mismo pues ahi en la sucursal de cesnav hicimos el tramite de grabacion, ahi nos dijeron que no se podia hacer otra vez y efectivamente lo intentaron pero no lo permitio el sistema por que ya se habia hecho con anterioridad.
regresamos a la oficina y me dijeron que no se podia hacer, que ellas,las personas que estan para atender que ellas solo estan ahi para orientar a la gente que llega a la oficina; que debiamos ir al issfam para hacer el tramite nuevamente, pero era el ultimo dia para hacerlo y les dije que tenian que darme una solucion, era ya la cuarta vuelta que daba con mi madre caminando que tiene 84 año y dificultad para caminar, entonces la señorita me dijo pues voy a ver si se puede, fue  la computadora ,realizo el tr+amite y me dio el folio, tardamos aproximadamente una hora dando vueltas hasta que me dieron el folio,cosa que podian haber hecho en los cinco primeros minutos que llegamos.
atentamente
maria del refugio duran loranca
53 36 25 70
missing_info_en: What happens if the system says when talking on the phone that you cannot pass the magazine, there is no procedure for that situation and in September that happened with my mother.
improvements_en: We had in September -not being able to pass the telephone review- that we had to go to the secretary of the navy, because our home (in coyoacan) is the easiest, we arrived at the attention office and the two people who are there told us that we had We had to go to the bank and do the recording process again, we went to the bank right there because there at the Cesnav branch we did the recording process, there they told us that it could not be done again and indeed they tried but did not allow it the system because it had been done previously. We returned to the office and they told me that it couldn't be done, that they, the people who are there to attend to them, are only there to guide the people who come to the office; that we had to go to the issfam to do the procedure again, but it was the last day to do it and I told them that they had to give me a solution, it was already the fourth round that I was walking with my mother who is 84 years old and having difficulty walking, so the Mademoiselle told me, well, I'm going to see if you can, it was the computer, I did the tr + amite and he gave me the page, it took us about an hour to walk around until they gave me the page, which they could have done in the first five minutes that we arrived. attentively maria del refugio duran loranca 53 36 25 70

improvements:
para poder realizar mejor este tramite, el usuario debera tener la opcion de agendar su cita por si mismo por internet;  admas de tener la opcion del call center para las personas que no tengan acceso a internet o no sepan usar la computadora.
tambien el sistema debe ser en tiempo real, tal vez con un delay de 10 minutos pero no mas. para encontrar la mejor fecha a la mejor hora, en el mejor lugar de conveniencia para el usuario. (en ese orden debera ser la busqueda de las opciones)
quitar la opcion en la politica de cancelacion de 24 a 48 hras y que se aplique a tiempo real. (10 minutos a lo mas)
con esto se reduciran los tiempos muertos o las citas perdidas, con la opcion de que alguien en la fila de sin citas pueda ocupar ese espacio de quien falto a su cita, jalando el num de folio del usuario que requiere atencion inmediata.
improvements_en: In order to better carry out this procedure, the user should have the option of scheduling their appointment by themselves online; in addition to having the option of the call center for people who do not have access to the internet or do not know how to use the computer. also the system should be in real time, perhaps with a delay of 10 minutes but not more. to find the best date at the best time, in the best place of convenience for the user. (in that order should be the search for options) remove the option in the 24-48 hour cancellation policy and apply in real time. (10 minutes at most) This will reduce downtime or missed appointments, with the option that someone in the row of no appointments can occupy that space of who missed their appointment, pulling the folio number of the user that requires immediate attention.

Meanwhile, I cannot advance in another process for my retirement due to this error. my name is jose ma martinez gutierrez (this is how it appears on my birth certificate) and by mistake it was written by jose maria martinez gutierrez and I can't fix it yet. until they deign first to answer the phone in my hometown and then in tijuana the person who attends the curp does the same. meanwhile I have spent in laps, time and despair. the situation is very exhausting. Hopefully they can speed up and in a single module it will be solved. Although they give you a month on hold, but when you return, the document is already in order. that they use technology for the benefit of citizens. thanks my email is mex.jmartinez@gmail.com. for your someone from this dependency can help me to solve this situation. hopefully and get a response. sugiero que esto funcione como los seguros que cubren al conductor y al auto sin importar el vehiculo que maneje. 

que al capacitador, dependiendo de su preparacion y experiencia, se le autoricen las areas en las que es apto para dar cursos y que mientras no se salga de las areas autorizadas, ya no sea necesario que este registrando curso por curso.
por ejemplo, si le autorizaron economia y administracion, el puede llevar a cabo todos los cursos para los que el sea competente siempre y cuando caigan en las areas de  economia y administracion.

improvements_en: 1. That the procedures can be done online without having to go in person. 2. That the registration as an external training agent covers the person, not the courses so that he does not have to be registering each course and filling you with documents every time. I suggest that this works as the insurance that covers the driver and the car regardless of the vehicle you drive.  that the trainer, depending on his preparation and experience, be authorized the areas in which he is apt to give courses and that as long as he does not leave the authorized areas, it is no longer necessary that he is registering course by course. For example, if you are authorized economics and administration, he can take all the courses for which he is competent as long as they fall in the areas of economics and administration.  Thank you.  greetings and blessings.  Best regards.  lci francisco morales tel. 01 (833) 3623175 telcel 8331087240 mail: leverage53@hotmail.com  p. d. there is an error in the dc-5 format in the section "type of request that it presents" since it says "modification of instructions template", it should say "modification of instructors template".

improvements: gracias por preguntar. no es justo para las personas que vivimos fuera de la ciudad de mexico que seamos obligados a ir a mexico para tramitar la cedula profecional, eso solo es una invitacion a que nos roben la ciudad de mexcico es la ciudad mas que mas roba a los mexicanos que van de otros estados y la verdad da miedo ir a hacer un tramite que cencillamente podria realizarlo por internet, pues por tratar de mejorar nuestra vida personal y la de nuestras familias al obtener la cedula profecional para aspirar a un mejor empleo, y al ir a la ciudad de mexico, no solo arriesgo a ser asaltado por los delincuentes si no que tambien pongo en riesgo mi vida y la de mi familia. la verdad no se si vale la pena el riesgo, gracias por su comprencion, y espero que algun dia en el futuro dejen de centralizar este tipo de tramites y permitan que los estados creescan gracias.
improvements_en: thanks for asking. It is not fair for the people who live outside the city of Mexico that we are forced to go to Mexico to process the professional ID, that is only an invitation to steal the city of Mexico, it is the city that steals the most from Mexicans. that they go from other states and the truth is scary to go to do a procedure that could easily be done online, for trying to improve our personal life and that of our families by obtaining the professional license to aspire to a better job, and by going To the city of Mexico, not only do I risk being assaulted by criminals, but I also put my life and that of my family at risk. I really do not know if it is worth the risk, thank you for your understanding, and I hope that someday in the future they will stop centralizing this type of procedure and allow states to grow thanks.

missing_info: ustedes ponen requisitos en la pagina y cuando uno llega piden documentos adicionales que nunca se mencionaron y que segun es a criterio de quien los revisa, y con una mala actitud le dicen a uno "pues vayase y cuanto tenga los documentos listos viene".  perdemos todo un dia de trabajo , tardan un mes en dar otra cita . ademas de que se tardan horas (literal) en atender y con niños pequeños es la locura.  la ultima vez llegue a las 8:30 y sali a las 3:30 sin pasaporte , tuve que regresar al dia siguiente (otro dia perdido de trabajo) la niña llorando porque tenia hambre pues todo los snacks que le habia llevado se los acabo, y eso porque presente una queja y aceptaron que tenia razon. 7 horas para un tramite no puede ser posible y aparte mala actitud de los empleados lo hace mas dificil
improvements: creo que deberian tener un criterio unificado o agregar todos los posibles escenarios que se puedan presentar y que documentacion se debe llevar, espero tomen en cuenta la sugerencia y me gustaria tener  seguimiento de esto, el proximo mes tengo cita para renovacion de pasaporte espero y sea mucho mejor que la primera vez y respeten la documentacion que dice en esta pagina.
missing_info_en: you put requirements on the page and when one arrives they ask for additional documents that were never mentioned and that according to the criteria of the person who is reviewing them, and with a bad attitude they say to one "well go away and when you have the documents ready you will come". We lose a whole day of work, it takes a month to make another appointment. besides that it takes hours (literally) to attend and with small children it is madness. The last time I arrived at 8:30 and left at 3:30 without a passport, I had to return the next day (another day lost from work) the girl crying because she was hungry because all the snacks she had brought her were finished, And that's because I filed a complaint and they accepted that I was right. 7 hours for a procedure cannot be possible and apart from the bad attitude of the employees it makes it more difficult
improvements_en: I think they should have a unified criteria or add all the possible scenarios that can be presented and what documentation should be carried, I hope you take into account the suggestion and I would like to follow up on this, next month I have an appointment for a passport renewal I hope and be much better than the first time and respect the documentation that says on this page.

improvements_en: They could add an explanatory introduction to the use of the funeral services of the issste, clarifying that, in addition to the services of the issste facilities, we can contract private services and that we will be reimbursed up to a limit of both. por este conducto me dirijo a usted con la intencion de hacer llegar una informacion de caracter relevante, la cual se hizo en diversas denuncias anonimas por seguridad de quienes suscribimos el documento, y que de manera muy extraña ahora se saben los nombres de los denunciantes, las denuncias eran por narco menudeo, trata de personas y venta de droga en lugares publicos, en esta semanadel 27 de marzo al 2 de abril del 2017  llegaron a varios domicilios de la calle 3 de san pedro de los pinos casi esquina con patriotismo,  en las denuncias anonimas que hicimos, investigando nuestros nombres y direcciones, gente de nacionalidad colombiana una de ellas quien dijo llamarse paty gonzalez, la cual llego con 8 hombres altamente armados, asi es; armados, quien de forma violenta a fuera de nuestros domicilios nos esperaron para decirnos que ya estabamos ubicados y que nuestras familias les iban a romper la madre ya que ellos eran una gonorrea, ignorando lo que significa,  y no solo eso que tenian un mensaje de la que dice llamarse yetziry madelein echeverry  revetty y su hermana que pronto regresaria a mexico para ajustar cuentas con cada uno de los que  denunciaron,  y que ya habia gente colombiana y venezolana en mexico para atender este asunto con gente de tepito, cuidando nuestras casas pero ademas de que nos levantarian  uno por uno, esta colombiana de nombre paty gonzalez, dijo que a ellas no les podian hacer nada ya que contaban con un grupo de narcotraficantes que hacian lo que ellas querian ademas de gozar de proteccion segun ella del gobierno de la ciudad de mexico, ya que el dueño de la pagina los tenia comprados a todos,  dicha pagina de prostitutas que se llama  zona divas, y que ademas de ser putas contaban con el apoyo de policias de la ciudad de  asi como federales, y que todos recibian dinero por la proteccion de ellos.

tan es asi que nosotros al hacer las denuncias la que dice llamarse  yetziry madelein echeverry  revetty se le vio llegar en diferentes autos como se hizo saber a vender droga y a dedicarse a la prostitucion, ahora nos vemos amenazados los de esta colonia por un grupo de extranjeros delincuentes, como colombianos y venezolanos en nuestros domicilios particulares, por que esta chica junto con una banda de zona divas de pagina de prostitucion abierta, quieren venir a nuestro pais a matar, secuestrar, extorsionar, prostituirse etc., bajo la amenaza de que si volviamos abrir la boca nos iban a matar, que eramos unos hijos de puta, y que ellos eran demasiado berracos que no le tenian miedo a nadie al final ellas contaban con gente del gobierno quien las protegiera,   queriendo controlar parte de la ciudad de mexico por que hasta el dia de hoy nunca se hizo detencion alguna a pesar de que se dio la direccion de ella y su hermana, esta tal paty gonzalez de origen colombiano, se hizo llamar la jefa, la cual contaba ya con personas que estuvieran al cuidado de cada uno de los que denunciamos hasta que llegara la tal yetziry madelein, para dejar en claro quien mandaba y que ademas de ser tan berraca junto con otras chicas con las que llego eran unas gonorreas, sin saber eso que significa y que de aqui en adelante ellos en esta zona de san pedro de los pinos como la napoles, la tenian perfectamente controladas.

es por ello que hacemos un llamado al h. comisionado nacional de migracion lic. ardelio vargas, ya que existe el temor fundado de que tomen represalias en contra de nuestras familias, ya algunos vecinos se han cambiado hasta de casa por el miedo a ser asesinados, y otros despues de vivir toda nuestras vidas desde abuelos padres y ahora hijos, tenemos que migrar a otro lugar por el miedo a que nos maten, por lo cual esperamos se investigue y no se les permita la entrada a esta persona como su hermana y con las personas que viene que son demasiadas, ya que son un peligro para nuestra sociedad, venezuela sufre una crisis enorme en todos los aspectos y las personas que se introducen a nuestro pais son efectivamente delincuentes de alto poder, asi como gente de origen colombiano que ahora quieren controlar este pais a punta de pistola y amenazas.

esperando de favor contar con su apoyo, le agradecemos sus finas atenciones.

alejandro samuel medina
arturo graduño
luis olmos
andrea hernandez jimena cortes

we made, investigating our names and addresses, people of Colombian nationality, one of whom said his name was paty gonzalez, who arrived with 8 highly armed men, that's right; armed, who violently outside our homes waited for us to tell us that we were already located and that our families were going to break their mother since they were gonorrhea, ignoring what it means, and not only that they the name of Paty González, said that they could not do anything to them since they had a group of drug traffickers who did what they wanted in addition to enjoying protection according to her from the government of the mexico city, since the owner of the page had bought them all, that page of prostitutes called divas area, and that besides being whores they had e The support of city and federal police, and that everyone received money for their protection.  so much so that when we make the accusations, the one who says her name is yetziry madelein echeverry revetty was seen arriving in different cars as she made herself known to sell drugs and dedicate herself to prostitution, now we are threatened by a group of foreigners in this colony Criminals, such as Colombians and Venezuelans in our private homes, because this girl, along with a gang from the divas of an open prostitution page, want to come to our country to kill, kidnap, extort, prostitute themselves, etc., under the threat that if We would open our mouths again, they would kill us, that we were motherfuckers, and that they were too angry that they were not afraid of anyone, in the end they had government people who would protect them, wanting to control part of the city of Mexico for that until today no arrest was ever made despite the address of her and her sister, this paty gonzalez of Colombian origin, called herself the Boss, who already had people who were in the care of each one of whom we denounced until the yetziry madelein arrived, to make it clear who was in charge and that in addition to being such a thug along with other girls with whom she arrived they were some Gonorrhea, without knowing what it means and that from now on they had it perfectly controlled in this area of ​​San Pedro de los Pinos like Naples.  that is why we call on h. national immigration commissioner lic. Ardelio Vargas, since there is a well-founded fear that they will retaliate against our families, and some neighbors have even moved home for fear of being killed, and others after living our entire lives from grandparents, parents and now children, We have to migrate to another place because of the fear that they will kill us, so we hope that they will investigate and they will not be allowed to enter this person as their sister and with the people who come that are too many, since they are a danger to our Society, Venezuela suffers a huge crisis in all aspects and the people who enter our country are effectively high-powered criminals, as well as people of Colombian origin who now want to control this country at gunpoint and threats.  Hoping please to count on your support, we thank you for your kind attention.  alexander samuel medina arturo gradño Luis Olmos Andrea Hernandez Jimena Cortes  ccp. to universal ccp. to millennium group ccp a day ccp. the excelsior

missing_info: le falta los requisitos reales que solicita cfe, ya que salen con cada cosa. por ejemplo la subestacion compartida son tantos los requisitos que dura un tramite entre 3 y 4 meses. si ya se tiene la autorizacion del dueño, y los documentos de las personas morales que tiene su contrato, porque solicitarlos otra vez los mismos documentos. tambien se condiciona el contrato a las firmas de terceros para poder obtener el contrato. es una perdida de tiempo ya que se tiene que enviar el convenio a diferentes partes de la republica para ser firmado. y ni siquiera te dan la oportunidad de realizar el contrato con cartas compromiso de entregarlos despues de firmados. y poder obtener el contrato lo mas pronto posible. pero la cfe es una pared  para poder resolver esto. no entiende razones y no te da ninguna solucion solo que esos son los requisitos y si no cumples con esto no hay contrato. tiene que ser un poco flexible con esto.
improvements: solicitar bien los requisitos a cfe, ya que salen con cada cosa.
missing_info_en: it lacks the real requirements that cfe requests, since they come out with everything. for example, the shared substation has so many requirements that a process lasts between 3 and 4 months. If you already have the authorization of the owner, and the documents of the legal entities that your contract has, why request the same documents again. The contract is also conditioned to the signatures of third parties in order to obtain the contract. It is a waste of time since you have to send the agreement to different parts of the republic to be signed. And they do not even give you the opportunity to make the contract with commitment letters to deliver them after they are signed. and be able to get the contract as soon as possible. but the cfe is a wall to solve this. He does not understand reasons and does not give you any solution, only that those are the requirements and if you do not comply with this there is no contract. you have to be a little flexible with this.
improvements_en: request the requirements well to cfe, since they come out with everything.

missing_info:
fui a tramitar el pasaporte de mi hijita (una bebita de 6 meses), presentando todos lo documentos que se indican en este portal. sin embargo, me rechazaron el tramite porque en la constancia medica emitida por mi pediatra, no se asento desde que fecha mi hija es paciente del doctor. este requisito no esta publicado en este portal, ni esta contemplado en el reglamento  de pasaportes y del documento de identidad y viaje o la normativa que ha emitido la sre en relacion con la expedicion de pasaportes. por lo tanto, la sre no esta facultada para exigir dicho requisito, puesto que no existe fundamento juridico que lo sustente y, por otro lado, al no encontrarse este requisito registrado en el registro federal de tramites y servicios, la sre viola el articulo 69-q de la ley federal de procedimiento administrativo, que señala que "las dependencias y los organismos descentralizados de la administracion publica federal, no podran aplicar tramites adicionales a los inscritos en el registro, ni aplicarlos en forma distinta a como se establezcan en el mismo, a menos que se trate de tramites:
i. previstos en ley o reglamentos emitidos por el ejecutivo federal en ejercicio de la facultad prevista en el articulo 89, fraccion i, de la constitucion. en este caso, salvo por lo dispuesto en la fraccion ii, solo seran exigibles a los interesados aquellos datos y documentos especificos que, no estando inscritos en el registro, esten previstos en ley o en los reglamentos citados;"
improvements: señalar todos los requisitos que deben contener los documentos que deben presentarse para realizar el tramite y señalar el fundamento juridico que lo sustenta.
missing_info_en: I went to process the passport of my daughter (a 6-month-old baby), presenting all the documents indicated on this portal. However, they rejected the procedure because in the medical certificate issued by my pediatrician, I have not been established since the date my daughter is a doctor's patient. This requirement is not published on this portal, nor is it contemplated in the passport regulations and the identity and travel document or the regulations issued by the sre in relation to the issuance of passports. therefore, the sre is not empowered to demand said requirement, since there is no legal basis to support it and, on the other hand, since this requirement is not registered in the federal registry of procedures and services, the sre violates article 69 -q of the federal law on administrative procedure, which states that "the dependencies and decentralized agencies of the federal public administration may not apply additional procedures to those registered in the registry, nor apply them in a manner different from that established therein , unless it involves procedures: i. provided for in law or regulations issued by the federal executive in exercise of the power provided for in article 89, section i, of the constitution. in this case, except for the provisions of section ii, only those data and specific documents that, not being registered in the registry, are provided by law or in the aforementioned regulations will be required from the interested parties; "
improvements_en: indicate all the requirements that must be contained in the documents that must be presented to carry out the procedure and indicate the legal basis that supports it.

improvements:
somos un grupo de habitantes de la comunidad rural de siqueros, municipio de mazatlan, y estuvimos yendo a mazatlan desde septiembre a capacitacion de este programa arraigate, y nos decepciona que no nos dieron tiempo suficiente para hacer el preregistro de proyectos en linea. por favor tomen en cuenta que somos marginados, como creen que tenemos acceso a internet?, a una computadora, escaner, a documentos como un excel para generar la curp, a tener actas de asamblea protocilizadas y escaneadas, y simplemente nos cierran la puerta cancelando los registros.
no creo que se cumpla con la finalidad del programa de apoyar a quienes no tenemos y realmente necesitamos esos apoyos para producir y generar empleos.
por favor apoyenos con citas en ventanilla para nuestra comunidad de siqueros, mazatlan sinaloa.
mi correo es ozunaadalberto@hotmail.com
improvements_en: We are a group of inhabitants of the rural community of Siqueros, Mazatlan municipality, and we have been going to Mazatlan since September for training in this arraigate program, and we are disappointed that we were not given enough time to pre-register projects online. please take into account that we are marginalized, how do you think we have access to the internet ?, to a computer, scanner, to documents such as an excel to generate the curp, to have minutes of assembly protocilized and scanned, and they simply close the door on us by canceling the registers. I do not believe that the purpose of the program to support those we do not have is fulfilled and we really need those supports to produce and generate jobs. please support us with appointments at the window for our community of siqueros, mazatlan sinaloa. my email is ozunaadalberto@hotmail.com

improvements:
mi nombre es asa ebba christina laurell. inicie mi tramite al inicio de noviembre del año pasado. finalmente me mandaron a la unidad de prestaciones economicas #5 en la cdmx. tengo un talon de recibido con fecha del 17 enero, 2017 sin no de control para unificacion de cuentas y correccion de datos . me informan que no tienen plazos para hacer el tramite y en consecuencia estan congeladas mis fondos en el pensionissste. es imposible llamar por telefono porque me mandan de regreso a la grabacion que pide la extension que es 25760. me parece inverosimil que no se puede resolver el problema. 
pueden mejorar su servicio telefonico por ejemplo permitiendo llamadas en espera señalando el tiempo aproximado y no cortandola.
improvements_en: my name is asa ebba christina laurell. I started my procedure at the beginning of November last year. finally they sent me to the economic benefits unit # 5 in the cdmx. I have a receipt received dated January 17, 2017 without a control number for account unification and data correction. They inform me that they do not have deadlines to carry out the procedure and consequently my funds are frozen in the pensionissste. It is impossible to call by phone because they send me back to the recording that asks for the extension that is 25760. It seems unlikely to me that the problem cannot be solved. They can improve their telephone service, for example by allowing calls on hold, indicating the approximate time and not cutting it.

missing_info:
mejoramiento en el proceso de qa para el despliegue de nuevos sistemas y aplicaciones para esta secretaria y sus anexos. no se identifica claramente ni de manera amigable el tramite que se desea, mucha informacion no necesaria y basura digital en las paguinas ed los submenues. plano y aburrido el diseno en general asi como falta de rehalce en los enlaces importantes. muy vaga la manera de solicitar evaluacion y recomendaciones. fallo la liga hasta el 3er intento. triste ver que los procesos de preintegracion y testing de los nuevos sistemas y aplicaciones no pasa por un riguroso proceso y control de calidad.
ojala un dia podamos ver en los portales gubernamentales sistemas y aplicaciones del nivel que se merece el pueblo mexicano y que en las licitaciones se vea el compromiso de los contratistas que se integran a estos proyectos trabajen realmente por mejorar lo que se tiene actualmente y no solo por ganar un proyecto en el gobierno para futuras alianzas.
improvements: segun las mejores practicas y los avances tecnologicos se puede mejorar en todo. pero al menos me gustaria ver mejoras en los flujos de los procesos de tramite como este que no deberian ser taan engorrosos. tengo 2 hrs para agendar cita en linea para una persona de la 3a edad por pasaporte perdido y no puedo. es vergonzoso que suframos de este tipo de lagunas. yo trabajo en it desde hace 20 anios y no puedo creer que esto pase aun con el presupuesto mas bajo que se tenga para este tipo de proyectos. hacer cita por telefono y llevar todo en papel parece seguir siendo la mejor opcion. da lastima y verguenza verdaderamente.
missing_info_en: improvement in the qa process for the deployment of new systems and applications for this secretary and its annexes. The procedure that is desired is not clearly or amiably identified, much unnecessary information and digital garbage on the pages of the submenus. flat and boring design in general as well as lack of redo on important links. the way of requesting evaluation and recommendations is very vague. the league failed until the 3rd attempt. Sad to see that the pre-integration and testing processes of new systems and applications do not go through a rigorous process and quality control. Hopefully one day we can see in the government portals systems and applications of the level that the Mexican people deserve and that in the tenders the commitment of the contractors that join these projects is seen to really work to improve what is currently available and not only for winning a project in the government for future alliances.
improvements_en: According to best practices and technological advances, everything can be improved. But at least I would like to see improvements in the flow of processing processes like this that should not be so cumbersome. I have 2 hours to schedule an appointment online for a person of the 3rd age for lost passport and I can not. It is shameful that we suffer from this type of gap. I have been working on it for 20 years and I cannot believe that this will happen even with the lowest budget available for this type of project. making an appointment by phone and carrying everything on paper seems to be the best option. truly hurts and embarrassed.

improvements:
he hecho una lista correcta (como en el ejemplo) de mi menaje, que hoy no fue aceptada. he recibido otro ejemplo como la lista tiene que ser. ahora no es "ropa" sino "ropa dama" - tengo abrir todo para verificar si no hay calcetines de mi esposa entre mis pantalones... etc etc

tengo una visa para residente permanente en mi pasaporte, que gane porque mostre que soy solvente. jubilarme en mexico fue mi sueno y estaba feliz cuando recibi la visa. he hecho una lista muy buena en espanol correcto y recibi hoy un tratamiento como si soy un imbecil.

es imposible hacer una mudanza con una cosa por cajon. toallas en un cajon? y ropa en otro? afuera de cualquier realidad - asi se aumenta el volumen por 100%. 

me siento asi:
mexico dice "tienes dinero y te invito para vivir conmigo!"
digo "gracias, fantastico, con gusto acepto tu oferta!"
pero en el momento, cuando la mudanza viene, la invitacion cambia de una manera como si soy un esclavo de mexico. 
desnudo me aceptan, pero no con menaje. 

mi sueno murio hoy en el consulado de mexico. y estoy demasiado triste... dar algo y robarlo despues es peor que nunca ofrecerlo.
improvements_en: I have made a correct list (as in the example) of my kitchenware, which was not accepted today. I have received another example as the list has to be. now it is not "clothes" but "lady clothes" - I have to open everything to check if there are no my wife's socks between my pants ... etc etc  I have a permanent resident visa in my passport, which I win because it shows that I am solvent. Retirement in Mexico was my dream and I was happy when I received the visa. I have made a very good list in correct Spanish and I received a treatment today as if I am an idiot.  It is impossible to make a move with one thing per drawer. towels in a drawer? and clothes in another? out of any reality - thus the volume is increased by 100%.  I feel like this: Mexico says "You have money and I invite you to live with me!" I say "thank you, fantastic, I gladly accept your offer!" But at the moment, when the move comes, the invitation changes in a way as if I am a slave to Mexico. Naked they accept me, but not with utensils.  My dream died today at the Mexican Consulate. and I'm too sad ... giving something and stealing it later is worse than ever offering it.

improvements:
me sucedio en mi umf:
acudi a mi cita con mi medico familiar la cual era a las 19:00 hrs. sin embargo el dr. iba un poco atrasado con las consultas por el numero tan grande de pacientes que somos pase a las 19:15 y sali a las 19:30 el medico me envio al optometrista para lo cual primero hay que pasar a la firma de autorizacion con el jefe de piso, esto me llevo 5 minutos posteriormente y al ser necesario fui al piso inferior de la umf ya que ahi esta el area de vigencia de derechos a pedir el sello precisamente de vigencia, y me encontre con la mala atencion y ademas trato despota por parte de los  funcionarios de ventanilla limitandose a decirme que "estaba fuera del horario de atencion y que ellos no tienen ninguna responsabilidad que esta es solo de los medicos" que tal? y nuestros derechos como derechohabientes del imss a recibir trato decoroso y oportuno ?? y como es posible que mejor los medicos esten dando atencion hasta las 20:00 hrs. y en vigencia de derechos solo hasta las 19:30 absurdo no? los medicos pasaron por una preparacion academica y el personal de ventanilla tendran acaso la preparatoria terminada??? por el trato dudo que tengan la secundaria, en fin yo creo que se deberia trabajar mas en la sensibilidad del servidor publico en escritorio y ventanillas y dejar de protegerlos a traves del sindicato ya que, al final son servidores publicos que pagamos los derechohabientes por medio de las aportaciones patronales y nuestros impuestos.
improvements_en: it happened to me in my umf: I went to my appointment with my family doctor which was at 7:00 p.m. however dr. I was a little late with the consultations because of the large number of patients that we are. I went at 19:15 and left at 19:30. The doctor sent me to the optometrist, for which first we must go to the authorization signature with the boss. of floor, this took me 5 minutes later and if necessary I went to the bottom floor of the umf since there is the area of ​​validity of rights to ask for the stamp of validity, and I found the poor attention and also despota treatment by part of the officials at the window just saying that "it was after hours and that they have no responsibility that this is only the doctors" how about? and our rights as imss beneficiaries to receive decent and timely treatment? and how it is possible that the doctors are better giving attention until 20:00 hrs. and in force of rights only until 19:30 absurd no? the doctors went through an academic preparation and the window staff will have the finished high school ??? Because of the treatment I doubt that they have high school, in short, I believe that more work should be done on the sensitivity of the public servant at desks and windows and stop protecting them through the union since, in the end, they are public servants that the beneficiaries pay through of employer contributions and our taxes.

a quien corresponda, tener solamente una linea telefonica para todo mexico no es un servicio suficiente para abastecer a toda la comunidad. la programacion de cita para el tramite de pasaportes, esta basada a dos medios que no estan en servicio la mayoria del tiempo. primeramente, la linea telefonica con el numero por descrito es: 01 800 8010 773 "no es un numero disponible". la unica website en linea internet es, mexitel.sre.gob.mx cual dicha  esta "actualmente no disponible para manejar esta solicitud". siendo estos los unicos dos medios de comunicacion para programar una cita de tramite, para un pasaporte mexicano no son suficientes para dar un servicio a todo un pais. 
espero que este mensaje sea escuchado en nombre de toda la poblacion que sufre por meses para poder contactar un representante o simplemente tener acceso a una red electronica. 
con sinceridad: poblacion mexicana. gracias.
improvements:
1. amplear mas lineas telefonicas, o por consulado seria beneficiario para todos.
2. manter una website diponible a todo momento seria bueno tanto para emplados como para compradores. 
-gracias.
missing_info_en: To whom it may concern, having only one telephone line for all of Mexico is not a sufficient service to supply the entire community. Appointment scheduling for passport processing is based on two media that are not in service most of the time. Firstly, the telephone line with the number described is: 01 800 8010 773 "it is not an available number". the only website online internet is, mexitel.sre.gob.mx which is "currently not available to handle this request". these being the only two means of communication to schedule an appointment, for a Mexican passport they are not enough to provide a service to an entire country. I hope this message is heard on behalf of the entire population that suffers for months to be able to contact a representative or simply have access to an electronic network. sincerely: Mexican population. Thank you.
improvements_en: 1. to use more telephone lines, or by consulate would be a beneficiary for all. 2. Maintaining a website available at all times would be good for both employees and buyers. -Thank you.

se recibio el miercoles 18 de mayo un oficio, el sgparn.03vs.2458/17, dirigido a andrea y lorena ros lechuga, en el cual la semarnat, delegacion federal en el estado de veracruz, comunica la revocacion del registro de uma por haber omitido la presentacion del informe anual de actividades por dos años y por no haber atendido el oficio sgparn.03.vs.6834/16 del 17/11/16, el cual nunca fue recibido.  al respecto se establecio comunicacion con la mesa de ayuda de gobmex, habiendo recibido un correo mediante el cual asignan el numero de ticket 323253 y el agente 14 da dos numeros telefonicos: 54900900 y el 54900988 (inexistente) para recibir atencion y ayuda.  el asunto es que despues de una docena de intentos a los numeros telefonicos y al conmutador  todas, absolutamente todas, las extensiones marcadas o son inexistenetes o mandan a un sistema de mensaje y no hay manera de comunicarse con persona alguna, ya sea en atencion ciudadana o en vida silvestre.
el presente correo es con el fin de obtener ayuda, ya sea por esta via, por telefono o mediante una cita, con quien sea responsable o a quien acudir, la cual no ha sido posible agendar, despues de varios intentos.
el caso es de que, efectivamente, no se presentaron los informes de actividades ya que el predio (rancho) fue invadido en noviembre de 2012, para lo cual los invasores obtuvieron una escritura totalmente ilegal y no fue sino hasta hace dos meses que se logro recuperar mediante acciones de caracter juridico la legal posesion del predio en cuestion, situacion que se puede demostrar con la demanda y juicio al respecto, por lo que se busca el apoyo de semarnat para que continue el registro en custion.
en espera de su apoyo, quedo de ustedes,
atentamente
rafael ros torres
apoderado de andrea ros lechuga.
cel.-5554160285

In this regard, communication was established with the gobmex help desk, having received an email through which they assigned the ticket number 323253 and agent 14 gave two telephone numbers: 54900900 and 54900988 (non-existent) to receive attention and help. the matter is that after a dozen attempts to the telephone numbers and the switch all, absolutely all, the extensions dialed or are non-existent or send to a message system and there is no way to communicate with any person, either in citizen attention or in wildlife. This email is for the purpose of obtaining help, either by this route, by phone or by appointment, with whom you are responsible or to whom you can go, which has not been possible to schedule, after several attempts. the case is that, in fact, the activity reports were not presented since the property (ranch) was invaded in November 2012, for which the invaders obtained a totally illegal deed and it was not until two months ago that it was achieved to recover through legal actions the legal possession of the property in question, a situation that can be demonstrated with the lawsuit and judgment in this regard, for which the support of semarnat is sought to continue the registration in question. awaiting your support, I remain from you, attentively rafael ros torres empowered by andrea ros lettuce. cel.-5554160285
